data.title: Finding away through peace
data.text: Came early so not to wake the peace of mine of others who live here. I walk through taking pictures in peace. It opens around 3:00pm park deep inside. Very interesting world of another side of life. Seen one person and said good morning with no answer. May she didn't understand so I went my way. I'll come back when they open. Yes they have Disabled parking. What else I don't know until I take a tour. Cost I guess it's a open ❤️

data.title: Take the tour, you'll be amazed~
data.text: Take the tour, you'll be amazed at what you'll learn. Lots of information is given to you on the tour of this unusually decorative building that is right off the freeway.
